quote.p:
$12 million for coarse cotton fabrics and perhaps other commodities
                                to be obtained from Japan through the barter of ECA cotton diverted
                                to Japan from the China Program;

$12.5 million for continuing support to the food rationing programs
                                in Canton and Swatow and for the initiation of new rationing
                                programs in the principal cities of Hainan Island;
